snippet.title: Superman | Sneak Peek
snippet.description:
Krypto, take us home. #Superman - Only in Theaters July 11

“Superman,” DC Studios’ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who’s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (“Twisters,” “Hollywood”) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (“The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel”) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the “X-Men” movies, “Juror #2”) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (“For All Mankind”), Anthony Carrigan (“Barry,” “Gotham”), Nathan Fillion (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “The Suicide Squad”), Isabela Merced (“Alien Romulus”), Skyler Gisondo (“Licorice Pizza,” “Booksmart”), Sara Sampaio (“At Midnight”), María Gabriela de Faría (“The Moodys”), Wendell Pierce (“Selma,” “Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan”), Alan Tudyk (“Andor”), Pruitt Taylor Vince (“Bird Box”) and Neva Howell (“Greedy People”).

“Superman” is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with editors William Hoy (“The Batman”), Jason Ballantine (the “IT” films, “The Flash”) and Craig Alpert (“Deadpool 2,” “Blue Beetle”).

“Superman” will be in theaters and IMAX nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Annies Kitchen Season 3 | Episode :99 |  Special Episode with Dhyan | Amrita TV
snippet.description:
Don't miss this delightful blend of food and heartfelt conversations! Hit LIKE, SHARE, and SUBSCRIBE for more amazing episodes! 🔔✨heese, and juicy chicken that will make your taste buds dance! 😋

Don’t miss this special episode of Annie’s Kitchen, packed with great food, engaging conversations, and a touch of nostalgia! ❤️

👉 Watch now and enjoy the feast!
📌 Like, Share & Subscribe for more exciting celebrity episodes! 🎥✨


"Annie's Kitchen" is a unique and exciting cookery-cum-chat show, airing every Friday at 8 PM on Amrita TV. In its second season, this delightful program is hosted by the multi-talented and charming Annie Shaji Kailas, a well-known actress in the Indian film industry. Join Annie as she whips up delicious and mouth-watering dishes in the kitchen, showcasing her culinary skills while inviting celebrity guests from the world of entertainment to join her.

                The show is divided into two engaging segments. In the first segment, watch as Annie demonstrates how to prepare a special dish, adding her personal touch and sharing handy cooking tips that will leave you craving more. In the second segment, the real fun begins! Annie sits down for a lively and entertaining chat with her celebrity guests, asking them humorous, intriguing  questions that reveal fascinating stories from their lives and careers.

                                         Annie, who is married to renowned filmmaker Shaji Kailas, brings a perfect blend of warmth and wit to every episode. Together, they have become a beloved couple in the industry, and Annie’s playful charm and insightful interviews make "Annie's Kitchen" a must-watch for viewers of all ages.

Money Pechu – April 4, 2025:

Markets turned volatile today as global uncertainties led to a sharp stock market crash, pulling down major players like Tata Motors, HDFC Bank, TCS, Reliance, Vedanta, Sun Pharma, Cipla, and Gensol Engineering. The Nikkei Index, Dollar Index, and Gift Nifty reflected the global selloff mood. Meanwhile, investors flocked to gold as a safe haven, pushing the gold rate today in Chennai to new highs. Tech giants like Google and Meta also saw pressure amid global market jitters and recession fears.

snippet.title: Manoj Kumar Death: 87 साल की उम्र में Manoj Kumar का निधन, फिल्मी सितारों ने दी श्रद्धांजलि!
snippet.description:
देशभक्ति फिल्मों के माध्यम से दर्शकों के दिलों में अलग जगह बनाने वाले हिंदी सिने जगत के दिग्गज कलाकार मनोज कुमार का 87 साल की उम्र में निधन हो गया। उन्होंने शुक्रवार सुबह मुंबई के कोकिलाबेन धीरूभाई अंबानी अस्पताल में अंतिम सांस ली। मनोज कुमार ने बॉलीवुड को उपकार, पूरब-पश्चिम, क्रांति, रोटी-कपड़ा और मकान सहित ढेर सारी कामयाब फिल्में दीं। इन फिल्मों की वजह से उन्हें दर्शक 'भारत कुमार' के नाम से भी जानते थे। मनोज कुमार के निधन से बॉलीवुड जगत में सन्नाटा पसर गया है। इस दुख की घड़ी में बॉलीवुड सितारे मनोज कुमार के घर उनको श्रद्धांजलि देने पहुंचे।

snippet.title: FilterCopy | Reality of a NEET Aspirant | Ft. Tanya Sharma, Ruma Mondal
snippet.description:
Being a NEET aspirant in India? It’s not just about books and mock tests—it's a whole emotional rollercoaster filled with anxiety, last-minute revision, relatives asking the wrong questions, and friends who mean well but say the weirdest things. 😩📚

In this hilarious and painfully relatable FilterCopy sketch, we dive into the reality of a NEET student’s life—the pressure, the panic, and of course, the people who keep saying things like:
👉 “Beta, NEET nikaalna toh easy hai na?”
👉 “Arey Sharma ji ka beta bhi kar raha hai!”
👉 “Tumhe toh doctor banne ka passion hai na?” 😐

From group studies that turn into therapy sessions to panic before results day, this one’s for all the NEET warriors out there fighting their way through syllabus, stress, and society. 😭✊

🎯 Tag a NEET aspirant who needs a laugh break!
💬 Drop a comment and tell us the most annoying thing someone said while you were preparing. 👇

Credits:
Title: Durga Chalisa
Singer: Lakhbir Singh Lakha
Music Director: Mahesh Prabhakar, Ashwani Panwar
Concept: Ashwani Panwar
Edit & Gfx: Prem Graphics PG
Label: Music Nova

Lyrics:
Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni
Namo Namo Ambe Dukh Harni
Nirakar Hai Jyoti Tumhari
Tihun Lok Phaili Ujiyari

Shashi Lalaat Mukh Maha Vishala
Netra Lal Bhrikouti Vikarala
Roop Maatu Ko Adhik Suhave
Darsh Karat Jan Ati Sukh Paave
Tum Sansar Shakti Ley Keena
Palan Hetu Anna Dhan Deena
Annapoorna Hui Jag Paala
Tumhi Aadi Sundari Bala

Pralayakal Sab Nashaan Haari
Tum Gouri Shiv Shankar Pyari
Shiv Yogi Tumhare Gun Gaavein
Brahma Vishnu Tumhein Nit Dhyaave
Roop Saraswati Ko Tum Dhara
De Subuddhi Rishi Munina Ubara
Dhara Roop Narsimha Ko Amba
Pragat Bhayi Phaad Kar Khamba

Raksha Kari Prahlad Bachayo
Hiranyaykush Ko Swarg Pathayo
Lakshmi Roop Dharo Jag Mahin
Shree Narayan Anga Samahin

Ksheer Sindhu Mein Karat Vilaasa
Daya Sindhu Deejey Mann Aasa
Hingalaja Mein Tumhi Bhawani
Mahima Amit Na Jaat Bakhani

Matangi Dhoomawati Mata
Bhuvaneshwari Bagala Sukhdata
Shree Bhairav Tara Jag Tarini
Chhinna Bhala Bhava Dukh Nivarini
Kehari Vahan Sohe Bhawani
Laangur Veer Chalat Agavani
Kar Mein Khappar Khadaga Virajay
Jako Dekh Kaal Darr Bhajey

Sohe Astra Aur Trishula
Jate Uthata Shatru Hiya Shoola

Nagkoti Mein Toumhi Virajat
Tihoun Lok Mein Danka Baajat
Shumbh Nishumbh Daanav Tum Maare
Rakta Beej Shankhana Sanghaare
Mahishasur Nrip Ati Abhimani
Jehi Agh Bhar Mahi Akulaani

Roop Karaal Kali Ka Dhara
Sena Sahita Tum Tihin Samhara
Pidh Pari Santana Par Jab Jab
Bhayi Sahay Maat Tum Tab Tab
Amarpuri Auro Sab Lokaa
Tab Mahima Sab Rahey Ashoka
Jwala Mein Hai Jyoti Tumhari
Tumhein Sada Poojey Nar Nari

Prem Bhakti Se Jo Jas Gaave
Dukh Daridra Nikat Nahin Aave
Dhyave Jo Nar Man Layi
Janma Maran Tako Chhouti Jaayi
Jogi Sur Muni Kahat Pukaari
Yog Nahi Bina Shakti Tumhari
Shankar Acharaj Tap Kinho
Kaamaru Krodh Jeet Sab Leenho

Nishdin Dhyan Dharo Shankar Ko
Kaahu Kaal Nahin Sumiro Tumko
Shakti Roop Ko Maram Na Paayo
Shakti Gayi Tab Mann Pachitayo
Sharnagat Huyi Kiriti Bakhai
Jai Jai Jai Jagadambe Bhawani

Bhayi Prasanna Aadi Jagadamba
Dayi Shakti Nahin Keen Vilamba

Maukon Maatu Kashta Ati Ghero
Tum Bin Kaun Hare Dukh Mero
Asha Trishna Nipat Satave
Ripu Murakh Mohi Ati Darpave
Shatru Nash Keejai Maharani
Soumiron Ikchit Tumhein Bhawani
Karo Kripa Hey Maatu Dayala
Riddhi Siddhi Dey Karahou Nihaala

Jab Lagi Jiyoun Daya Phal Paun
Tumharo Jas Mein Sada Sunaun
Durga Chalisa Jo Koi Gaavey
Sab Sukh Bhog Parampad Paave

Devidas Sharan Neej Jaani
Karahun Krupa Jagadambe Bhawani
Karahun Krupa Jagadambe Bhawani

Sharanagat Raksha Kare
Bhakt Rahe Nishank
Me Aaya Teri Sharan Mein
Matu Leejiye Ank

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

The men finally clean the premises and are relieved. The effects of strenuous work are showing and Jethalal feels tired. Meanwhile, Popatlal thanks the ladies for making them clean their respective houses. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1523
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Jetha Aur Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTAUo34hpXVbh1keqAyhuhj

This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Aas Paas Last Mega Episode Part - 02 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 2nd April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

snippet.title: M3GAN 2.0 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
oops! she did it again!
#M3GAN2 is only in theaters June 27. 

---
Website: http://www.M3GANmovie.com
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/universalpictures  
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/meetM3GAN/
X: https://twitter.com/meetm3gan
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/M3GAN/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/m3gan


The murderous doll who captivated pop culture in 2023 is back. And this time she’s not alone. 

The original creative team behind that phenomenon—led by horror titans James Wan for Atomic Monster, Jason Blum for Blumhouse and writer-director Gerard Johnstone—reboot an all-new wild chapter in A.I. mayhem with M3GAN 2.0. Two years after M3GAN, a marvel of artificial intelligence, went rogue and embarked on
a murderous (and impeccably choreographed) rampage and was subsequently
destroyed, M3GAN’s creator Gemma (Allison Williams) has become a high-profile author and advocate for government oversight of A.I. Meanwhile, Gemma’s niece Cady (Violet McGraw), now 14, has become a teenager, rebelling against Gemma’s overprotective rules.

Unbeknownst to them, the underlying tech for M3GAN has been stolen and misused by a powerful defense contractor to create a military-grade weapon known as Amelia (Ivanna Sakhno; Ahsoka, Pacific Rim: Uprising), the ultimate killer infiltration spy. But as Amelia’s self-awareness increases, she becomes decidedly less interested in taking orders from humans. Or in keeping them around. 

With the future of human existence on the line, Gemma realizes that the only option is to resurrect M3GAN (Amie Donald, voiced by Jenna Davis) and give her a few upgrades, making her faster, stronger, and more lethal. As their paths collide, the original A.I icon is about to meet her match.

M3GAN 2.0 is written and directed by acclaimed returning filmmaker Gerard Johnstone, from a story by Gerard Johnstone and Akela Cooper, based on characters created by Akela Cooper & James Wan.

The film co-stars returning cast members Brian Jordan Alvarez and Jen Van Epps as Gemma’s loyal tech teammates, Cole and Tess, and new characters played by Aristotle Athari (Saturday Night Live, Hacks), Timm Sharp (Apples Never Fall, Percy Jackson and the Olympians) and Grammy winner and 11-time Emmy nominee Jemaine Clement (Avatar: The Way of Water, What We Do in the Shadows). 

Produced by James Wan, Jason Blum and Allison Williams, the film is executive produced by Gerard Johnstone, Adam Hendricks, Greg Gilreath, Michael Clear, Judson Scott and Mark D. Katchur. 

The first M3GAN film shattered box office records, opening to $30.4 million domestically to become the biggest opening weekend for a PG-13 horror film since A Quiet Place Part II. The film went on to gross more than $180 million worldwide.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Aamar Boss | Official Teaser | Nandita Roy | Shiboprosad Mukherjee | Raakhee Gulzar | Windows
snippet.description:
২২ বছর পর, আবারও বড় পর্দায় অভিনেত্রী রাখী গুলজার। নন্দিতা রায় এবং শিবপ্রসাদ মুখোপাধ্যায়ের পরিচালনায় একটি অনবদ্য মা ও ছেলের গল্প, 'আমার বস'; আসছে ৯ই মে।
'Aamar Boss' is slated to release on 9th May 2025. 

‘Aamar Boss’ is a modern family drama explores a unique idea: an office-based old-age crèche started by the boss's mother. This innovative setup boosts employee productivity while creating a more caring, inclusive workplace.

Cast:
1.    Raakhee Gulzar
2.    Shiboprosad Mukherjee

snippet.title: ऐसे मैं Army में पहुँची और 34 की उम्र में… @MajorKhushbooPatani | Inspirational | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Apply to become speaker at Josh Talks - https://bit.ly/4iDHrxt

यह कहानी Khushboo Patani की है, जो भारतीय सेना में मेजर के पद से रिटायर हुई हैं। उन्होंने अपने जीवन के संघर्षों और चुनौतियों को साझा किया है, जो उन्हें आत्मविश्वास और साहस से भरपूर बनाते हैं। उनकी यात्रा बरेली से शुरू होती है, जहां उन्होंने अपने माता-पिता के समर्थन से शिक्षा में उत्कृष्टता हासिल की। वह बताती हैं कि कैसे उन्होंने अपने डर को पार किया और आत्म-विश्वास के साथ आगे बढ़ीं। उन्होंने अपने अनुभवों में मानसिक स्वास्थ्य, बुलिंग और आत्म-सम्मान के मुद्दों पर चर्चा की। उन्होंने बताया कि कैसे उन्होंने अपने जीवन में कठिनाइयों का सामना किया और भारतीय सेना में शामिल होने का निर्णय लिया। उनका मानना है कि हम जितनी अधिक चुनौतियों का सामना करते हैं, उतना ही मजबूत बनते हैं। 

भारतीय सेना में अपनी सेवा के दौरान उन्होंने न केवल खुद को चुनौती दी, बल्कि दूसरों की मदद करने, शांति स्थापना और संघर्षों को सुलझाने के लिए भी काम किया। उनके अनुभवों ने उन्हें यह सिखाया कि जब तक हमारी आंतरिक शक्ति मजबूत होती है, तब तक कोई भी मुश्किल हमें पराजित नहीं कर सकती। उनकी कहानी यह संदेश देती है कि हम कभी भी विक्टिम नहीं होते, बल्कि हम हमेशा अपने जीवन की चुनौतियों का सामना करने वाले सैनिक होते हैं। उन्होंने यह भी बताया कि कैसे उन्होंने शांति स्थापना के कार्यों में भाग लिया और दूसरों की मदद करने का प्रयास किया। अंत में, उन्होंने युवाओं को प्रेरित किया कि वे अपने आंतरिक आवाज़ पर विश्वास करें और जीवन में सकारात्मक बदलाव लाने के लिए आगे बढ़ें। यह कहानी न केवल प्रेरणादायक है, बल्कि यह मानसिक स्वास्थ्य के महत्व को भी उजागर करती है।

This is the story of Khushboo Patani, a former Major in the Indian Army, who retired after years of dedicated service. She has shared her journey, filled with struggles and challenges, which shaped her into a person full of confidence and courage.

Her journey began in Bareilly, where she excelled in education with the support of her parents. She speaks about overcoming fear and self-doubt, and how she moved forward with determination. Throughout her experiences, she has addressed important issues like mental health, bullying, and self-respect. She shares how she faced hardships in life and ultimately decided to join the Indian Army. According to her, the more challenges we face, the stronger we become.

During her service in the Indian Army, she not only pushed her own limits but also worked towards helping others, maintaining peace, and resolving conflicts. Her experiences taught her that as long as our inner strength remains intact, no obstacle can defeat us.

Her story carries a powerful message—we are never victims, but warriors fighting the battles of life. She also shared how she participated in peacekeeping missions and made efforts to help those in need.
In the end, Khushboo Patani encourages young people to trust their inner voice and take bold steps to bring positive change in life. Her story is not only deeply inspiring but also highlights the importance of mental health and resilience.

snippet.title: Anjali मिली अपने माता-पिता से! | Iss Pyar Ko Kya Naam Doon Ek Baar Phir
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe *Star Plus* : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-LPIU24bQXVljUXivKEeRQ

Click Here To Download The JTN - Dayan Slayer Game : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.GameInstitute.JaaduTeriNazar&utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=description&utm_campaign=game 

Yeh kahaani hai free-spirited Astha ki, joh apne sapno ke saath jeeti hai! Jab uski mulaqaat hoti hai khadoos Shlok se, dono ki duniya badal jaati hai! Par jab Astha ko Shlok ki perfect family ke andar ki sachai pata chalti hai, toh unki zindagi ek naye mod par aa jaati hai! Kya pyaar aur dard ke beech woh ek doosre ko samajh paayenge? Kya woh de paayenge apne iss pyaar ko koi naam?

Karate Kid: Legends unites the iconic martial arts masters of one of the most beloved film franchises of all time to tell a completely new story full of action and heart. When kung fu prodigy Li Fong (Ben Wang) relocates to New York City with his mother to attend a prestigious new school, he finds solace in a new friendship with a classmate and her father. But his newfound peace is short-lived after he attracts unwanted attention from a formidable local karate champion. Driven by a desire to defend himself, Li embarks on a journey to enter the ultimate karate competition. Guided by the wisdom of his kung fu teacher, Mr. Han (Jackie Chan), and the legendary Karate Kid, Daniel LaRusso (Ralph Macchio), Li merges their unique styles to prepare for an epic martial arts showdown. 

Directed by: Jonathan Entwistle   
 
Written by: Rob Lieber    

Produced by: Karen Rosenfelt
          
Executive Producers:
Jenny Hinkey
Ralph Macchio

Cast:
Jackie Chan and Ralph Macchio
Ben Wang
Joshua Jackson
Sadie Stanley
Ming-Na Wen

snippet.title: The Infinite Intelligence | By Sandeep Maheshwari
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

snippet.title: Sikandar Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Sikandar Salman Khan Comeback Movie Directed by AR Murugadoss with Rashmika Mandanna is totally wasted opportunity with Old Mass & Funny Emotions combined with Slow Salman Khan Action & Bigger than life poor presentation.

Sikandar Full Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma with Positives & Negatives would be shared in this Video. Bollywood Biggest Fanbase Star Salman Khan actually tried his best or Another chance would be needed for Much Awaited Comeback? Find Clear answer inside!

Sikandar is a 2025 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film directed by A. R. Murugadoss and produced by Sajid Nadiadwala. The film stars Salman Khan in the titular role, alongside Rashmika Mandanna, Sathyaraj, Kajal Aggarwal, Sharman Joshi, Prateik Babbar, Kishore, Jatin Sarna and Sanjay Kapoor. In the film, Sanjay "Sikandar" Rajkot, the king of Rajkot, becomes a target for Minister Rakesh Pradhan after killing his son. When his wife’s donated organs save three lives, Rakesh seeks revenge, forcing Sanjay to protect them.

The film was officially announced in April 2024. Principal photography commenced the following June in Mumbai and wrapped by March 2025. The film has songs composed by Pritam, background score composed by Santhosh Narayanan, cinematography handled by Tirru and editing by Vivek Harshan. With an estimated production budget of ₹200 crore, it is one of the most expensive Indian films of all time.

Sikandar was theatrically released worldwide on 30 March 2025, in standard and IMAX formats, coinciding with Eid al-Fitr.

नमस्ते दोस्तों!

आज के The Ranveer Show हिंदी के 353rd Episode में हमारे साथ हैं Dr. Prerna Kohli, एक अनुभवी Clinical Psychologist जिनके पास 30 वर्षों का गहरा अनुभव है Mental Health, Loneliness और Self-Awareness के क्षेत्र में।

इस Episode में हमने बात की है कि कैसे Loneliness आज के समय की सबसे बड़ी mental challenges में से एक बन चुकी है। Dr. Prerna ने बेहद आसान और दिल छू जाने वाले शब्दों में बताया कि अकेलेपन को कैसे समझा जाए, और किस तरह से Self-Talk, Therapy, Community Living और Physical Wellness के ज़रिए इससे बाहर निकला जा सकता है।

यह बातचीत हर उस इंसान के लिए है जो अपने अंदर झाँकना चाहता है, खुद को बेहतर समझना चाहता है, और Emotional Well-being की ओर एक मजबूत कदम बढ़ाना चाहता है।

ऐसे ही और अर्थपूर्ण episodes के लिए देखते रहिए The Ranveer Show Hindi, सिर्फ़ Ranveer Allahbadia के साथ।

Hello friends!

In today's 353rd Episode of The Ranveer Show Hindi, Dr. Prerna Kohli, an experienced Clinical Psychologist with over 30 years of experience in the field of Mental Health, Loneliness and Self-Awareness.

In this episode, we talk about how loneliness has become one of the biggest mental challenges of today's times. In very simple and heart-touching words, Dr. Prerna explains how to understand loneliness, and how to overcome it through Self-Talk, Therapy, Community Living and Physical Wellness.

This conversation is for everyone who wants to look inside themselves, understand themselves better, and take a strong step towards Emotional Well-being.

For more such meaningful episodes, keep watching The Ranveer Show Hindi, only with Ranveer Allahbadia.

Movie : Deewane Huye Pagal (2005)
Star Cast : Shahid Kapoor, Akshay Kumar, Sunil Shetty, Paresh Rawal

मूवी : दीवाने हुए पागल (2005)
स्टार कास्ट: शाहिद कपूर, अक्षय कुमार, सुनील शेट्टी, परेश रावल

नमस्ते दोस्तों!

आज के The Ranveer Show हिंदी के 352nd Episode में हमारे साथ हैं Palga Rinpoche, एक Buddhist Monk, जिन्होंने Buddhism, Karma, Forgiveness और Spiritual Growth के विषय में गहरी समझ साझा की। यह Episode न केवल Self-Reflection और Acceptance की बात करता है, बल्कि Life Transformation और Inner Peace की ओर भी मार्गदर्शन देता है।

Palga Rinpoche के साथ इस बातचीत में हम जानेंगे Karma, Anger और Forgiveness का महत्व, और Meditation की शक्ति के बारे में। साथ ही यह भी समझेंगे कि कैसे Spiritual Practices हमारी मुश्किलों को एक अवसर में बदल सकती हैं।

यह Hindi Podcast उन सभी के लिए एक अनमोल अनुभव है जो Self-Healing और Inner Growth की राह पर चलना चाहते हैं।

ऐसे ही Meaningful Hindi Podcasts के लिए देखते रहिए The Ranveer Show Hindi, सिर्फ़ Ranveer Allahbadia के साथ।
